"    signed up by text message.  You should give your contact details, and "
"ask for\n"
"    theirs, so you can stay in touch as you carry out your pledge.  If "
"anybody\n"
"    signs your pledge later, the last message that you sent will be "
"automatically\n"
"    forwarded to them, and they will be given a link to read older messages."
